children.content: The general idea of life events is to invert governments traditional perspectives. It means moving away from an administration that modernizes along its own needs, procedures and organizational settings (inside out), instead moving toward an administration that wants to understand how citizens experience and perceive the whole chain of interactions with the administration during important events in their lives (outside in).

"Sammenhengende tjenester er tjenester der flere (offentlige) aktrer har ansvar for deler av en og samme tjeneste ut mot brukeren. Brukeren opplever en sammenhengende tjeneste som en smidig brukerreise der hun fr lst sitt behov uten mtte forholde seg til at det er flere virksomheter som eier tjenestene formelt sett".
